summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5666 for the improvement of The Alley in Block 8, D. T. Denny's Water Front Addition, being the Alley between 3rd Avenue West and 14th Avenue West, from West Harrison Street to West Republican Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 74958, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
